EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO EDUCATION -- CURRICULUM
***
1 This act would provide that any school teaching sexual education to students shall provide
2 the sexual education curriculum to every parent or legal guardian with a child in that school, and
3 the parent or legal guardian shall consent, in writing, to the teaching of such sexual education
4 curriculum to their child.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
